Well, Dr. Hyeon also said he was going there to look into something.

00:39:52.307 --> 00:39:54.434
- I guess you can tag along. - Ah.

00:39:55.435 --> 00:39:57.312
Okay, be safe.

00:39:57.979 --> 00:39:59.062
Okay, Ms. Hwang.

00:39:59.063 --> 00:40:00.565
Mmm. Right then.

00:40:03.484 --> 00:40:06.904
Gosh, these are so dry. Got to eat them faster.

