People must be swimming in money or something.

00:41:19.477 --> 00:41:21.353
Are they out of their

00:41:21.354 --> 00:41:23.814
What is it even made of?

00:41:23.815 --> 00:41:24.816
Damn it.

00:41:30.780 --> 00:41:34.534
DON'T SKIP YOUR MEALS, DR. DO

00:42:04.355 --> 00:42:06.523
Jiui, can you spare me a moment?

00:42:06.524 --> 00:42:08.401
