00:42:26.669 --> 00:42:31.423
JANGMOKDO DOCK

00:42:31.424 --> 00:42:35.928
JANGMOKDO, PYEONDONGDO

00:42:37.388 --> 00:42:38.597
- Hello. -  Oh my, hello.

00:42:38.598 --> 00:42:40.557
- You're from the Pyeondong Health Center? - Yes.

00:42:40.558 --> 00:42:42.392
I've been waiting for you.

00:42:42.393 --> 00:42:44.895
I'm Lee Seongu from the Jangmok Health Center.

00:42:44.896 --> 00:42:46.855
- Hello. - Thank you for your cooperation.

00:42:46.856 --> 00:42:49.024
Not at all. The helipad's this way.

00:42:49.025 --> 00:42:50.443
- Right this way. - Right.

00:42:51.944 --> 00:42:53.445
Mind your step.

00:42:53.446 --> 00:42:55.573
I heard the chopper couldn't land.

00:42:56.449 --> 00:42:57.532
Right.

00:42:57.533 --> 00:43:01.536
They rushed the construction so much that they didn't have a lighting setup,

00:43:01.537 --> 00:43:04.748
And the helipad was so disorganized that the chopper couldn't land.

00:43:04.749 --> 00:43:07.751
Was the Pyeondongdo incident also caused by lighting issues?

00:43:07.752 --> 00:43:09.586
We're not sure yet.

00:43:09.587 --> 00:43:11.630
They're still investigating.

