00:43:17.595 --> 00:43:22.641
I heard those bastards told them to only transfer the patients by boat.

00:43:22.642 --> 00:43:25.770
What the hell can we do on an island when they block off the air routes?

00:43:26.813 --> 00:43:27.980
Lighting

00:43:33.569 --> 00:43:37.280
Would you mind giving us that doctor's contact information?

00:43:37.281 --> 00:43:38.532
Sorry?

00:43:38.533 --> 00:43:40.034
On the day of the accident

00:43:41.994 --> 00:43:45.123
I don't think I saw any lights at the helipad either.

00:43:48.709 --> 00:43:49.793
Yes, hello.

00:43:49.794 --> 00:43:52.337
I'm Yuk Hari, a nurse at the Pyeondong Health Center.

00:43:52.338 --> 00:43:55.257
I'm looking into lighting issues at helipads in Yeopoong-gun.

00:43:55.258 --> 00:43:57.926
Hello. I'm Hyeon Chiyeon, a PH doc at Pyeondong.

00:43:57.927 --> 00:44:00.303
I heard they built a new helipad there recently.

00:44:00.304 --> 00:44:02.931
